description:
A murder in Southside leaves a home abandoned&ndash;except for the strange noises coming from the cellar&hellip;

What Lies Within is a scenario for 1-5 investigators in which a murder is only the beginning of the inexplicable occurrences in one Arkham mansion. Investigators will explore a murder scene, fend off terrible creatures, encounter strange phenomena, and investigate the noises coming from the cellar of the supposedly empty house. They must discover why the victim was murdered&ndash;and what he did with his life before it was so violently ended&ndash;in order to leave the mansion alive.

&mdash;description from the publisher

Alex and Alice, kids with superpowers, notice that their friends have become unbearable and are acting oddly. And that&rsquo;s right after the superpopular amusement park &ldquo;Lollipop Inc.&rdquo; opened in their city. So, when their secret agent parents are given the task to infiltrate the park, the kids are certain to catch the opportunity of conducting their own investigation&hellip;

Lollipop Inc. is an exciting tabletop quest created especially for kids. Open new locations and complete the mission by solving original puzzles, sometimes by completely unconventional means. Find the villain and uncover his evil plans in this standalone Unfold Kids game.

&mdash;description from the publisher

The noble kingdom of Rohan has a long history of war, and the aftermaths of those wars can still be felt today in the unquiet dead of the marshes to the East and in the grudge held by the Dunlendings to the West. Now, an avaricious enemy has set plans in motion from the shadows, and you and your fellow heroes must uncover the conspiracy before Rohan is plunged into war once more&hellip;

The Scourges of the Wastes Figure Pack for The Lord of the Rings: Journeys in Middle-earth can enhance both the Spreading War campaign and the Poison Promise downloadable campaign. This pack contains three beautifully-sculpted new miniatures of the primary villains of the two campaigns, as well as five new item cards and a new role that can be used in any Journeys in Middle-earth adventure. No collection would be complete without it!

description from publisher's website

Leland inspired everyone around him, even friends and neighbors. Though nobody seemed to learn the exact same lessons&hellip;

This 3-card expansion mixes up your memories by adding 2 new Lesson cards. These are shuffled in with the deck and then 2 random Lessons are removed, making your day on the lake less predictable. These Lessons also feature an option with a mandatory movement direction, giving you less control over your boat.

It also includes an additional double-sided Family card, adding two new characters with their own goals to complete.
